Very super simple sway rice.

used programs: sway, tofi, kitty, fish, yazi, mako, helium (browser), kde kwallet/authentication agent, swaybg

Keybinds:
`MOD+(/shift)+num` to change/move to workspaces
`MOD+q` to open kitty
`MOD+r` to open tofi (runner)

And not much else important!

The sway stacked mode is pretty cool btw
